          "verseIndex": 0,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 5
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "物尚進則失安，故曰，企者不立。",
        "source": "cham"
      },
      {
        "id": "wangbi-2",
        "range": {
          "type": "range",
          "scope": "verse",
          "verseIndex": 1,
          "start": 0,
          "end": 40
        },
        "kind": "commentary",
        "text": "其唯於道而論之，若郤至之行，盛饌之餘也。本雖美，更可薉也。本雖有功而自伐之，故更為肬贅者也。",
        "source": "cham"
      }
    ]
  },
